| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4511 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: fa7951cf-584e-5f56-8568-8dca9ef29832"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
